    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the efficacy and assess the safety of CD07805/47 gel
      0.5% applied topically once daily for 29 days versus vehicle control, in subjects with
      moderate to severe chronic persistent vascular facial erythema
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
